              "coded_information": [
                "DECAY"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The contribution of each half-life to an X-ray",
                "peak was extracted by linear optimization of the",
                "experimental peak area decay with an analytical",
                "expression of a multicomponent decaying peak.",
                "The corresponding electron-capture branching ratios",
                "and internal conversions and the fluorescence yields",
                "of the X-rays, not given in the text, were taken from",
                "literature."
